  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0bc6\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b9e\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baf \u0bae\u0bca\u0bb4\u0bbf \u0b86\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bb2\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Korean teacher dies in highway accident",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Aturugiri Traffic Control Station reported that a luxury jeep carrying a Korean language teacher collided with a lorry loaded with tiles on the Colombo Ring Road yesterday night (23) in Sappukaskanda area. The jeep driver sustained minor injuries and the Korean language teacher died on the spot.",
        "Githani Manel Priyanthi (47 years) of Konahena Veedhi, Gadawada, Rammuthugala, a mother of one died in the accident.",
        "Police said that the accident took place when a truck loaded with tiles was going from Matara towards Gadava when a luxury jeep coming from behind in the same direction collided with the back of the truck.",
        "After the jeep crashed into the lorry, which turned into a pile of debris, the teacher was injured beyond recognition, police said.",
        "According to the police, the accident took place about two kilometers away from the mouth of the pass.",
        "The police investigation has revealed that the accident was caused by the driver's carelessness and excessive speed.",
        "Investigations are being conducted on the recommendation of Chief Inspector MS Ashoka Kumara, Station Commander of Athurigiriya Traffic Control Station."
      ],
